      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">3. Time management</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Managing time effectively is crucial when working on a capstone project. To overcome this challenge, students can create a schedule, set deadlines for each task, and prioritize tasks based on their importance.</p>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">4. Lack of motivation</h3>
